<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٥٥٤٠ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ، عَنْ قَتَادَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ فِي قَوْلِهِ:</span> <span class="c3">{أَوْ آخَرَانِ مِنْ غَيْرِكُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[المائدة: ١٠٦]</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«مِنْ أَهْلِ الْكِتَابِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>